{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_scave_set_1", "eventName": "硬幣的意志", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "硬幣的意志", "storyInfo": "受羅德島雇用後不久，清道夫在一次任務中意外遇見了當年暗算自己的仇人。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "砸碎我家窗戶的人，就是這個女孩嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "嗯，入室行竊的話，根據族群的規矩，確實應該被沒收所有東西，扔到荒地上去......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "不過她只是從儲藏室拿走了一塊乾乳酪而已呀。嘿，你叫什麼名字？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "哈莫琳......這樣吧，哈莫琳，我用扔硬幣來決定你的命運吧。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "如果是數字的這一面朝上，你就要被趕走；如果是頭像這一面朝上，我就放過你。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cherunder_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......報告。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......第七天。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天早上又有死者被處理掉了......建築內部的環境源石顆粒密度應該很高，感染者狀況惡化很迅速。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近二十四小時內，依然沒有看到工廠員工在高牆未遮擋的區域活動，更沒有人從大門離開工廠。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走到稍微更靠近工廠的地方，通訊信號就會受到強烈干擾。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工廠外圍是高壓電網，控制室的位置暫時無法確認。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高牆附近守衛的換班時間和巡邏規律已經摸清楚了。內部警備情況還沒辦法知道。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒是想快點把手頭的事情做完，你同意的話，我可以採取最暴力的手段。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哼，羅德島有自己的做事風格，我明白。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一個方案？每天凌晨三點，工廠的廢料運輸載具會進入地下層，排汙管道會暫停使用。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴上防毒面具的話，從那裡走沒問題。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反正，我只負責癱瘓這裡的安保系統，後續的接應和引導不歸我做，對吧？", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道。必要的時候，可以做得不那麼清白乾淨。你們叫我來處理這件事，就是為了這個吧。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彙報完畢。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這家叫羅德島的雇主，竟然真的想救感染者......", "name": "清道夫"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽到載具出入口開啟的噪音了......該出發了。", "name": "清道夫"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G08", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "afrom": 0.0, "rfrom": 0.0, "gfrom": 0.0, "bfrom": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 12.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃——", "name": "工廠守衛"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你先昏一會兒吧。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的安保系統看起來簡直像監獄的一樣複雜......算了，本來也是差不多的地方。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要在驚動其他人之前找到控制室——", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小心！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再往前走就要觸發自動報警了——", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——啊？怎麼是你？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tense_intro", "key": "$tense_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......圖利奧。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“清道夫”，呵，竟然還活著......", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼會出現在這裡？小老鼠，既然你拿著武器，你是從哪條下水道爬進來的？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——等等，先把刀放下，我們好好說話。不然，我要拉響警報了。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的系統是連接到警察局的，任何警報都會被視作感染者失控的信號。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你也是這裡的警備人員？", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，但是相信我，清道夫......", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，相信你？", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們現在的目標應該是一致的。我看到你把那個守衛放倒了，你在找出去的路，對吧？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也想逃出去，不然我剛剛不會拉你一把。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼......", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真的，這幾年我已經洗心革面啦。你看，我現在也是感染者了，我也經歷了很多慘事，我......理解你。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你都鑽進這家工廠了，應該也知道這裡的情況了。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我是所謂的警備人員，但被關在這裡的所有人，境遇都沒什麼差別。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你明明在監管他們。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道這家工廠是用很多好聽的說辭把感染者騙來的......我也不想這樣，但要活命就不得不做一些沒那麼體面的事情。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別指望我會同情你。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，還有最重要的......我對這裡的安保系統很熟悉。沒有我幫忙，你逃不過那些監控。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有兩處監控中心在同時監管整個工廠的狀況。通過切斷總閘的方式來中斷監控是行不通的，工廠會迅速切換到應急電源。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你必須找一個同伴，當然，我也必須有人幫忙。所以無論你有多不信任我，至少我們現在最好的做法就是暫時合作。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我沒說我要逃出去。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你防備著我，但是......", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——我要讓這裡的安保系統完全癱瘓。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我接的委託就是這樣。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪有雇傭兵會直截了當把委託任務告訴別人？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別廢話。我想快點把工作做完，告訴我監控中心的位置。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好吧，這算是達成合作了吧？你是這個意思吧？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你的打算，清道夫。我不會直接告訴你所有路線的。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們走這邊，靠著牆根走。我已經確認過監控死角了。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工廠負責人在這裡嗎？", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不在，當然不在，這都已經凌晨三點多了。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只是偶爾出現。一個健康的人是不會想在源石顆粒密度這麼高的環境中生活的。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡都是感染者？", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。對你來說沒什麼區別吧？你都已經感染了，再接觸幾個也無所謂。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的同夥呢？應該做好防護準備了吧。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們想要什麼？工廠裡沒什麼值錢的東西，這裡的源石製品精度也不高。我真想不通你們為什麼要來這種地方偷東西。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......什麼都不回答啊。以前跟你談生意的時候，你可沒這麼難溝通。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖說你要是還和以前一樣的話，大概也沒法在雇傭兵這行活下來。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別問多餘的事情，也別廢話。我可沒那麼想跟你這種東西當同夥。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嘁。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在我們不得不當同夥了。從這裡我們要分頭往兩邊走。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穿過工作室，那邊就是監控中心。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就十分鐘後各自動手，之後我會去找你。會合之後我們再去總控室處理整個安保系統。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你最好是真的洗心革面了。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "其實那枚硬幣落下來的時候，我是知道哪一面會朝上的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "來，把手伸出來，我教你，像這樣——", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "沒事的，哈莫琳，你雖然感染了，但也不用離我那麼遠的。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "是啊，以後就更遠了......明天早上你就要從這裡離開了吧？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "抱歉......這件事，我也沒辦法左右。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們都知道你是為了族群的生存資源而感染的，可是族群卻不肯留下你......是啊，只是為了生存下去就不得不冒險，一直都是這樣。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "作為留念，收下這枚銀幣吧。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "無論在哪裡，無論發生什麼......我希望你能活下去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_prison_commandroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "基地台信號遮罩儀已經關閉了。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，高壓電網......斷電。電動大門......開啟。拉下總閘。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "完成了？——", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "jump", "xpos": 100.0, "power": 0.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "jump", "power": 5.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖......！我就知道！", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1#6$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "jump", "power": 0.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "jump", "xpos": 100.0, "power": 5.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這傢伙！又想暗算我？！", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1#6$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這對你有什麼好處？", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1#6$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，總得試一下吧？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你覺得你能得手嗎？我總不至於被你這種小人欺騙第二次！", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然我該做什麼？就這麼等著你把我殺掉？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在你我都不需要同伴了，工廠的大門敞開，誰都可以輕鬆逃走。比起當被害者，我當然選擇先下手。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒說我要殺你。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你當然不會說。但你怎麼可能放過我？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在也是感染者了，我知道你當初有多走投無路了......也知道你該有多恨我了。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是啊，能讓我記住臉的委託人可不多。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "jump", "power": 0.0, "times": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 20.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，札拉克竟然能有這麼大力氣......", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 100.0, "fadetime": 0.9, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說過，你不可能得手的。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別動，不然這把刀就砍下去了。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖......", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你該搞清楚了，現在殺不殺你全由我自己的心情。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......這該死的礦石病黏上了我，讓我變得虛弱，你怎麼還安然無恙？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是怎麼做到的......你完全變了一個人。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，你當然會希望我還是剛開始做雇傭兵時的樣子，單純，好騙。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幹了件沒人願意做的髒活，卻沒有從委託人那裡拿到任何報酬。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為礦石病發作而痛到失去意識，在陰溝裡醒來，發現自己僅有的家當也被順手拿走。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時我以為你活不久了，所以我想物盡其用......", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，物盡其用。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在刀尖上過日子的人，不都是默認要這麼互相利用的嗎？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且我又能做什麼？等著一個感染者死掉並且在我面前造成擴散感染？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰能想到你活下來了，而且一直活到今天？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是啊，可能因為有人希望我活下去。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我醒來的時候，縫在衣服裡的那枚銀幣還在，所以我決定活下去。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這隻老鼠的生命力可真頑強。一枚銀幣能換到什麼？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不用它換什麼。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你是怎麼......", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像你被騙到這座工廠來，以為這裡會給感染者提供相對穩定的生活，結果面對的卻是惡劣的生存環境和非人的待遇。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我經歷的也無非就是這些，可能更差一點。但生活就是這樣。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你那是什麼口氣......說得就好像我跟你是一樣的東西......", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家都是一樣。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哈，我懂了，你看到我現在的樣子，是不是很想嘲笑我？是不是有一種報復的快感？難怪你沒那麼生氣。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘁......想得可真多。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，就是你讓我落到今天這個境地的！", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是因為找上了你這個感染者雇傭兵，沒過多久我也跟著出現了礦石病的症狀。我從一開始就該遠離感染者！", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這傢伙最好搞清楚，平時接觸到感染者可不會讓你得礦石病。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得我會相信這種話？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒什麼興趣糾正你的想法，只不過這是我現在雇主的看法，我得替他們這麼說。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哦，難怪你害怕我復仇，卻還是要讓我當你的“同夥”。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想讓我幫你逃出去，然後處理掉我，完成你想像中的“復仇”。你所謂的“物盡其用”。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，難道你不是這麼想的嗎？你一路上配合我，不也是等著現在下手？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到這時候還廢話什麼，還要我教你這地方是怎麼處理死掉的感染者的嗎？", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我跟你合作，只是為了快點完成我的委託任務。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能忍受惡劣的工作環境，這也包括能忍受惡劣的同夥。我可不會像你一樣想東想西的。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，這次我的任務是協助救出感染者，而你也是感染者。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救出感染者？開什麼玩笑......", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......算了，問問雇主吧。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......報告。", "name": "清道夫"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工廠安保系統已經癱瘓，但負責人不在園區內。", "name": "清道夫"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我不關心你們要怎麼把那些感染者救出去，或者要把他們帶去哪裡。我只想確認，我的任務算不算完成。", "name": "清道夫"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工廠的守衛也是感染者，這種人你們也要救嗎？", "name": "清道夫"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......所以，我可以用自己的手段處理這方面的麻煩。", "name": "清道夫"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明白。我會儘快撤離到指定地點。", "name": "清道夫"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彙報完畢。", "name": "清道夫"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼......看來他們真的打算說到做到。", "name": "清道夫"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放在以前，我可不信會有什麼可靠的委託人，更不會相信有把感染者當一回事的傢伙......", "name": "清道夫"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......就像她的願望不可能實現一樣。", "name": "清道夫"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——不過，你也聽到了，他們給了我一點自由。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1#4$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......還真是除了雇主的要求什麼都不想啊。", "name": "圖利奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_149_scave_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......既然你覺得我什麼都不想，那我用扔硬幣來決定你的命運吧。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1#7$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是數字的這一面朝上，我就把你這垃圾清理掉；如果是頭像這一面朝上，我就放你走，讓你像其他感染者一樣，重新開始生活。", "name": "清道夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_149_scave_1#7$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "清道夫摸出了那枚小小的銀幣，拋向空中。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "曾經許多次，她在孤獨無助的時候，閉上眼睛將一切寄託於擲硬幣的結果。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“也許有一天，你不用為活著本身拼盡全力的時候，你就會去想自己要往哪裡走吧。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她不知道像她這樣的人會不會有那一天。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但這一次，她知道硬幣的答案。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}